  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The current study investigates the effects of tDCS in patients with multiple sclerosis (MS).
      The investigators hypothesize that anodal tDCS will increase motor performance in patients
      with MS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
